        "text": "=You are a customer support classifier.\nClassify the following email as either \"FEEDBACK\" or \"ISSUE\".\n\nFEEDBACK = appreciation, product reviews, suggestions, testimonials, NPS responses.\nISSUE = complaints, errors, bugs, billing problems, account access, abuse reports.\n\nReply with ONLY one word: FEEDBACK or ISSUE.\n\nEmail subject: {{$json.subject}}\nEmail body: {{$json.bodyText}}",
        "batching": {}
